Welcome on the LogWEx site

 LogWEx stands for Logging Extras for Web Applications. It aims to provide some utilities in order to enhance logging in
 Web applications. It is an extension for {{{http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2/}Log4J}}, and helps to add the
 <<session id>>, the authenticated <<user name>> ans some other pieces of information to yousrs logs.

 LogWEx has two modules : LogWEx core and LogWEx example.  LogWEx core is the main module which you can use in your
 deployment. LogWEx example is a small Web application which shows how to use LogWEx ; we are using it for some
 integration tests.
 